metadata.name: Metadost Avatar: In Deep Vibration
metadata.description:
This Metadost Avatar:
In Deep Vibration, from the Metadost Avatar Collection, guides you to the spiritual powers within you, and connects you to the Oneness of ALL that was, is, and will be.
Allow it into your present time and space. Focus, meditate with the vibrations of this infinite entity, and enter into the frequency of your Higher Self with this Avatar.
